# zlib CVE-2023-45853 — marked "will_not_fix" by Debian 12.
# Debian considers this low-impact and will not backport a patch.
# The affected code path (zipOpenNewFileInZip4_6) is not exercised
# by our runtime at all, since we don't process zip files in-app.
CVE-2023-45853

